	"dialogue":[
		{
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Detective Stone, Agent Pryce, glad to have the two of you here. I'll give you a brief update on the Esposito case.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "locationMarker",
                    "text": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -20
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 1,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -60
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "We interviewed Freddie Silva after you cracked the last case, and we learned a lot.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 0
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Adrian Esposito, a recognized crime lord and underworld kingpin, has always managed to act with discretion and stay just clean enough to stay under the radar.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "According to Freddie, he has somehow managed to create a massive drug-running network right under our noses, and we didn't have a clue.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "It seems that he's been carefully using a system of proxies to minimize information leakage, and we have no solid evidence against him.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "I'm assigning the ICORPS unit to investigate this operation and dig up solid evidence as to how it works and who the key players are.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Did Freddie give us any more to go off of? We're going to need a lead to start the investigation.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Again, due to the nature of the operation's proxy system, Freddie was only able to give us one name. Gerard Little.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Gerard Little is a technician working for the Future*Tech company right here in San Francisco.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 2
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "He's stationed at one of the terminals where the Future*Tech autonomous vehicle fleet is maintained.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Oh, the self-driving vehicle network? I actually rode one of those cars into the city from the airport.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 3
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "I didn't realize that it was maintained by a single company.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Yeah actually. Future*Tech has been using the city as a test bed for their innovations for quite some time now.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "The autononmous vehicle fleet has been a crowning achievement of theirs.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "It's definitely made the commute a lot easier. I certainly don't miss getting aggravated over congested traffic.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Ah yes, in regards to Future*Tech, they've agreed to assist us with the investigation. Here, take this phone.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 3,
            "statement": "Hello investigators, this is Nole Walker speaking. I'll be lending a hand in getting to the bottom of this affair.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 4
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Wait, Nole Walker? THE Nole Walker?",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 4,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -20
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 1,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -60
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Do you know who this is?",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -20
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 1,
                    "expression": 4,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -60
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Nole Walker is the CEO and founder of Future*Tech. He's a bit of a local legend.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -20
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 1,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -60
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Is there any particlar reason for your direct involvement as the contact for this investigation?",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 3,
            "statement": "Haha yes, when this came to my attention I felt that it was so important that I had to see to it personally.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 3,
            "statement": "Just use this phone to reach me at any point of the investigation and I should be able to fill you in should you have any questions about Future*Tech and our technologies.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 3,
            "statement": "Good luck.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 3,
            "statement": "...",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Ah yes, one more important thing.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Esposito has shown himself to be adept at avoiding incrimination in the past.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "We are concerned that he is a flight risk and that he may try to escape our grasp should he catch wind of our doings prematurely.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "We have taken him in for questioning for an unrelated charge but can only hold him here for so long.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Complete the investigation swiftly, this is our best chance of putting him away for good.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Head out to the Future*Tech maintenance terminal immediately.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Yes comissioner.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Will do.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "transition",
            "scene": 1,
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "locationMarker",
                    "text": "Maintenance Terminal"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Wow, look at all these cars.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "locationMarker",
                    "text": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
